==English==

===Pronunciation 1===
*[[IPA|IPA]]
**([[received pronunciation|RP]]): /təʊl/ or /tɒl/
**(General): /tɒʊl/ or /tɒl/

===Noun===
'''toll''' ([[tolls]])
# A [[fee]] for using something, esp. of roads and bridges
# Loss or damage incurred through a disaster
#:''the war has taken its toll on the people''

====Derived terms====
*[[toll road]]
*[[toll bridge]]
*[[toll booth]]
*[[tollgate]]

